title: Sonia, Rahul meet top Congress leaders; Prashant Kishor draws up strategy for 2024 polls - The Indian Express
content: Sonia, Rahul meet top Congress leaders; Prashant Kishor draws up strategy for 2024 polls  The Indian ExpressView Full coverage on Google News
description: The Congress leaders were also learnt to have discussed the party's strategy for the assembly polls in Gujarat and Himachal Pradesh scheduled for later this year and holding the party's 'Chintan Shivir' in Rajasthan this month.
